FreezeAt.name: FreezeAt
FreezeAt.description: Sets the frozen cells in the active worksheet view. The range provided corresponds to the cells that will be frozen in the top- and left-most pane.

params.name: frozenRange
params.description: A range that represents the cells to be frozen.

FreezeColumns.name: FreezeColumns
FreezeColumns.description: Freezes the first column or columns of the current worksheet.

params.name: count
params.description: Optional number of columns to freeze, or zero to unfreeze all columns.

FreezeRows.name: FreezeRows
FreezeRows.description: Freezes the top row or rows of the current worksheet.

params.name: count
params.description: Optional number of rows to freeze, or zero to unfreeze all rows.

GetLocation.name: GetLocation
GetLocation.description: Returns a range that describes the frozen cells in the active worksheet view.
